About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • If you only have one HDMI to HDMI cable, and you want to connect a flat-panel digital camera or another device with a micro HDMI port to a high-definition TV or computer screen with an HDMI interface, then this Micro HDMI to HDMI adapter cable will be your best choice. Note: Please check if your device is equipped with Micro HDMI port before purchase
  • Support HDMI 2.0: This Micro HDMI to HDMI Adapter supports HDMI 2.0 4K/3D, backwards compatible with previous versions, Audio Return Channel, 1440p and 1080p Full HD Resolution, and Ethernet Channel. It delivers both high-definition video and uncompressed multichannel digital audio into 1 cable for many home theater needs
  • Extreme Durability: Featuring the combination of gold-plated connectors, copper conductors, foil and braid shielding, high-quality aluminum housing, this male to female Micro HDMI cable is durably built for clear signals, minimal interference and physical strain
  • Wide Compatibility: This Micro HDMI adapter is compatible with GoPro Hero 7 Black, Hero 6 Hero5, Hero 4 Silver, Hero 3 White, Hero3+, Go Pro Hero 2018, Raspberry Pi 4, Sony A5000 handycam, Sony A6500 A6000 A6400 A73 A7S camera, Nikon b500, Canon EOS M50, IdeaPad Miix 300 Tablet, Ideatab Miix 700, IdeaTab Lynx K3011, ThinkPad 10 8, Yoga 2 Pro 3 ultrabook, Yoga 700 710, 710s, ZenBook UX305UA. Note: It can not fit for Samsung phone or tablet with Micro USB
  • Convenient & Portable: This male-to-female adapter cable provides spare or replacement units for different equipment. Portable with the length of 10 inches, convenient to take it anywhere you want, plug and play, easy to use

Climate Pledge Friendly

Climate Pledge Friendly uses sustainability certifications to highlight products that support our commitment to help preserve the natural world. Time is fleeting. Learn more

PRODUCT CERTIFICATION (1)

Compact by Design (Certified by Amazon) products remove excess air and water, which reduces the carbon footprint of shipping and packaging.

Compact by Design is a new sustainability certification created by Amazon to identify products that, while they may not always look very different, have a more efficient design. With the removal of excess air and water, products require less packaging and become more efficient to ship. At scale, these small differences in product size and weight lead to significant carbon emission reductions.

Learn more about this certification

Product Description

UGREEN Micro HDMI to HDMI Adapter Cable

UGREEN Micro HDMI to HDMI Adapter helps you to connect your phone, tablet, digital camera and other devices with Micro HDMI interface to an HDTV or A Computer Screen with an HDMI interface, which enables you to play games on your big-screen HDTV display or share high-definition video with your family.

Ultra High Definition

The Micro HDMI 4K adapter cable can transmit 4K videos at 60Hz, which is 4 times clearer than 1080P. It enables fluid details and an impressive viewing experience.

Wide Compatibility

Compatible for hero 7 black, hero 6 black, GoPro Hero (2018), hero5 black, HERO4 Black Silver, hero 3 Silver White Hero3 Black Edition, HERO3+ Black and Silver Editions.

Compatible for Raspberry Pi 4, Sony a5000 Handycam, Sony A6000 camera a6400 a6500, Sony A73 A7S, Nikon b500, Canon EOS M50.

Compatible for IdeaPad Miix 300 10" Tablet, Ideatab Miix 700, Miix 2 (10-inch) Tablet, MIIX 3-1030, Miix 2 11, Miix 710, Ideatab Miix S6000, IdeaTab S6000 Tablet, IdeaTab Lynx K3011, ThinkPad 10 ThinkPad 8.

Compatible for Yoga 2 Pro, Yoga 3 Pro ULTRABOOK, Lenovo Yoga 700, Yoga 710, Lenovo 710s, Lenovo N20P Chromebook, ZenBook UX305UA, UX430UQ, Transformer Mini T102HA laptop.

Package Contents

UGREEN Micro HDMI (Type D) to HDMI (Type A) Adapter x 1

Read more

Multiple Shielding

Multiple shielding protects against RF/EM interference, keeping a clear signal with little bandwidth loss for high performance.

Male to Female Adapter

This Micro HDMI to HDMI cable helps you to connect your phone, tablet, digital camera and other devices with a micro HDMI interface to an HDTV or A Computer Screen with an HDMI interface

Durable Nylon Braided

Built with premium gold-plated connectors and high-quality nylon braided jacket, this Micro HDMI cable is more durable and flexible, which ensures a longer lifespan.
